Randy and Jodi Speidel, from Bellefontaine, Ohio, created online fundraisers begging Good Samaritans for financial help .
Mrs Speidel wrote on GiveFroward.com that they had been living without gas all winter, had no running water and were close to having their electricity and Internet service shut off .
The couple's landlord found a note warning passersby of carbon monoxide poisoning caused by two charcoal grills they had dragged into their bedroom .